    {
        "content": "<p>By putting your cursor right before the <code>by</code> in /3 you can see the goal,</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code>    <span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"n\">b</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">ℚ</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">h</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"bp\">+</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"bp\">*</span> <span class=\"n\">b</span> <span class=\"bp\">&lt;</span> <span class=\"mi\">0</span>\n    <span class=\"bp\">⊢</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"mi\">0</span> <span class=\"bp\">-</span> <span class=\"n\">a</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">/</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"bp\">-</span><span class=\"n\">a</span> <span class=\"bp\">/</span> <span class=\"mi\">2</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
